  "repo_truth": "Review the exact 53-path worktree subject against baseline fd6242fbab911eebb09a4d541a6e5e1e32dc5468. No implementation proof wall or control-pack closeout byte is in this preliminary subject. The two help snapshots and the mounted Windows checkout use CRLF, so the broad WSL CLI surface has 87/103 passing and 16 known CRLF-only snapshot/pipeline byte-comparison failures; do not treat that explanation as approval.",
