    "Review every production and test byte in the exact baseline-to-worktree diff against HCM-2.1.",
    "Run bounded read-only Rust, filesystem, security, portability, and scope checks as needed.",
    "Return findings first with exact file and line evidence and the smallest valid in-scope remediation."
  ],
  "non_goals": [
    "No edits, staging, commits, dispatch/handoff/ledger writes, or user task hops.",
    "No definition, schema asset, kind, profile, descriptor, Cargo, pipeline, stage, SDK, Tauri, Substrate, adapter, contract, dock, or HCM-2.2+ change.",
